{"tid":1747514,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你可以控制既唔止你自己既一票","createTime":"2019-11-23T09:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T09:35:44.000Z","uid":341572,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"afd8c394f196fc5095b0f66fbb79f0fef43278a9","tid":1747514,"uid":341572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:00:40.000Z","msg":"黃既方接既唔洗講 一定出黎投 <br />\n但係如果自己身邊既藍絲屋企人唔去投票<br />\n咁就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最直接既方法就係幫佢保管身份證明文件<br />\n要知道老人家無記性 我地後生既幫佢保管咁重要既野好應份<br />\n大部分都無咁神心搞呢搞路去證明自己有投票資格去投票<br />\n又可以做一日孝子 自己一早去投票之後就帶佢飲茶/行山/行商場<br />\n共享天倫之樂 票站聽日發生咩事無人知<br />\n咁危險點可以叫屋企人冒險呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之達到目標就係勝利<br />\n唔好太多道德包袱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54bcb19524585672ae132c78d9ae77cc9c7781ef","tid":1747514,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:26:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>"},{"pid":"9c96383158a4fbe70535d45a74f8b38323b046f8","tid":1747514,"uid":282836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:35:44.000Z","msg":"【11-24 告急】 投本土泛民，不投建制，連登每小時245留言討論投對家，有圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ScLG1qp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FScLG1qp.png&h=c6d3bd0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ezKeyS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ezKeyS</a>"}]}